LEWANDOWSKI v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [H. C. No. 107,

September Term, 1957.]

Decided June 11, 1958.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

Per Curiam.

These applications for leave to appeal from two denials of writs of habeas corpus are denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Allen in the court below.
